          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蒼穹大陸，天道宗修煉場。大比剛結束，弟子們紛紛回洞府閉關。林逸也回了洞府——然後躺下了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "大比結束後，林逸回到洞府，盤腿打坐。這是他第一次認真嘗試修煉。趙小七正好路過。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "好，來試試這個世界的修煉是怎麼回事……等等，系統面板上怎麼多了一個按鈕？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "「自動修煉腳本」？這什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "哦——打坐就等於掛機啊！那我不需要自己操作？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "按下去試試……嗯，靈力開始自動運轉了。太好了，本來就不想動。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "師兄！你剛才說「不想動」——這是「以不動應萬動」的境界嗎？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "不是，我就是懶。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "師兄太謙虛了！您一定是在進入深層修煉狀態！我來替師兄守門，絕不讓任何人打擾！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "隨便你，我先睡了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "林逸設定好自動修煉腳本，靈力開始以不可思議的速度自動運轉。然後——他躺下睡覺了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "三天後。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "睡得真舒服……嗯？系統通知？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "「恭喜升級！當前等級：Lv.52」……什麼？！我睡一覺升了五十級？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "林逸！老夫來看看你的修煉進——"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "這……這股靈壓！你、你突破了金丹期？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "哦，蕭長老。對啊，掛機三天就升了五十級。效率還行吧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "掛……掛機三天……升了……五十……級……？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "對啊，照這個速度，我睡個幾個月不就全服第一了嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "全……全服……？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老雙腿發軟，扶著門框勉強站穩。林逸並不知道，這個「隱藏加成」的數值，已經超越了大陸所有修行者的總和。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene3",
    "file": "04-content3.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "三天！我在師兄洞府外守了三天三夜！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "師兄臨入定前說了——「隨便你，我先睡了」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "這是何等境界！「先睡」——指的是先讓肉身沉寂，讓元神獨自運轉天道！「隨便你」——是說凡間之事已不值得他操心！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "老夫親眼所見……三天，他就從鍛體期到了金丹期……"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "我的觀察日記已經超過十萬字了。標題是《林逸師兄閉關悟道全紀錄——論天道與呼吸的關係》。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "十……十萬字？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老，你剛才也看到了吧？師兄親口說「掛機三天，效率還行」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "「效率」——師兄用一個詞就概括了修煉的本質！天道運轉，本就是最高效的法則！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "不可能！老夫修行三百年才到元嬰期！他三天就……"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老臉色鐵青，渾身顫抖。當晚，他回到自己的洞府，翻出了修行三十年的功法筆記。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "老夫這三十年的功法……在林逸面前，不過是廢紙。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "然後，他把功法燒了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
